title: NJPW Superhuman Taiji Ishimori Gets Ridiculous One More Time
overview: NJPW Superhuman Taiji Ishimori Gets Ridiculous One More Time was a professional wrestling pay-per-view (PPV) produced by New Japan Pro-Wrestling and Taiji Ishimori that took place on November 12, 2025 at Shinjuku FACE in Tokyo, Japan.
